OL,6,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak has
OL,7,Flaunched a new free childcare scheme
OL,8,Ffor England to allow eligible families
OL,9,Fof children from nine months will be
OL,10,Fable to claim 15 hours of free
OL,11,Fchildcare.
OL,13,FThe government claims it will save
OL,14,Ffamilies almost #7,000 a year, however
OL,15,Fa number of providers say they don't
OL,16,Fhave the spaces or staff to deliver
OL,17,Fthe funded hours, and parents worry
OL,18,Fthe scheme won't save them as much
OL,19,Fmoney as the government promised.
