OL,6,FEligible families of children as young
OL,7,Fas nine months old in England will be
OL,8,Fable to claim 30 hours of free
OL,9,Fchildcare a week by September 2025
OL,10,Funder the offer.
OL,12,FThe scheme is due to be rolled out in
OL,13,Fthree parts, with the first phase
OL,14,Fbeginning on Monday, April 1, as 15
OL,15,Fhours of free childcare is offered to
OL,16,Fworking parents of two-year-olds.
