OL,4,CEnglish provision extended
OL,6,FMeanwhile in Northern Ireland, there
OL,7,Fis no free childcare, and surveys show
OL,8,Fthat the average cost of annual
OL,9,Fchildcare for kids aged 0-4 in NI is
OL,10,Fover #14,000.
OL,12,FThe newly reformed NI Executive has
OL,13,Fstated that a childcare strategy is a
OL,14,Ftop priority.
