OL,4,CEnglish provision extended
OL,6,F"It's crucial that our political
OL,7,Fleaders grasp the urgency of the
OL,8,Fsituation and take action to address
OL,9,Fthe escalating costs that are
OL,10,Fburdening families across Northern
OL,11,FIreland," she said.
OL,13,F"Despite assurances from the
OL,14,FExecutive, we're witnessing a
OL,15,Ftroubling lack of tangible progress,
OL,16,Fleaving families feeling abandoned and
OL,17,Foverwhelmed.
