OL,6,F"The stories we've collected paint a
OL,7,Fstark picture of the challenges
OL,8,Ffamilies are enduring, our Executive
OL,9,Ftalk about economic prosperity ` with
OL,10,Fthousands of parents forced to
OL,11,Fconsider leaving the workforce because
OL,12,Fchildcare costs more than their wages
OL,13,F` this crisis effects everyone from
OL,14,Fthe NHS workforce to local business.
OL,16,F"We cannot afford to stand idly by;
OL,17,Fimmediate intervention is needed to
OL,18,Fsupport families, struggling childcare
OL,19,Fproviders and ultimately keep parents
OL,20,Fin jobs they've worked hard for."
